{
  "texts": [
    "Ultimately, we completed the 4-bit quantization P-Tuning v2 fine-tuning on a single RTX3090Ti GPU, consuming approximately 8 GB of GPU memory, making it accessible for most researchers to deploy locally.",
    "Furthermore, we have made the original dataset used in this study publicly available on our GitHub repository for reference and use by other researchers.",
    "However, this study has certain limitations.",
    "Firstly, the relatively small parameter size of the foundation model and the data scale used may result in errors such as the inclusion of English characters in the generated Chinese text.",
    "To address this issue, we plan to experiment with larger-scale foundation models and incorporate manual evaluation methods to ensure higher quality."
  ]
}